    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it spotless and pampered, so it\u2019s ready for a brand-new home. It drives like a total dream and is easily the cleanest one you'll find out there. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
